{{Quote|These are the Woodoos. They're our youngest students.|Luke Skywalker, to Chaf'orm'bintrano|<ref name="DN I">''[[Dark Nest I: The Joiner King]]''</ref>}}
The '''Woodoos''' were an [[Jedi Initiate/Legends|initiate]] training clan of the [[New Jedi Order]] that was usually made up of children between the ages of five and seven depending on species.<ref name="DN I" /> This clan was named after the [[Woodoo/Legends|Woodoo]], a creature native to [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] the Woodoo Clan, along with the rest of the students, were taken hostage during the [[Battle of Ossus (Second Galactic Civil War)|raid on the Jedi Academy]]. They were later rescued and taken to the [[Jedi Outpost]] on [[Endor/Legends|Endor's Sanctuary Moon]].

